48
00:02:28,524 --> 00:02:31,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Tell this Eight-Six kid</b></font>

49
00:02:31,364 --> 00:02:35,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>that I'll be waiting here
next Saturday at 10 p.m.</b></font>

50
00:02:35,234 --> 00:02:37,594
