53
00:03:00,254 --> 00:03:02,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Go for it, Takumi!</b></font>

54
00:03:02,024 --> 00:03:04,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Duct tape or whatever...</b></font>

55
00:03:04,224 --> 00:03:08,164
