87
00:05:08,084 --> 00:05:11,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Leave the wheel there and come out.</b></font>

88
00:05:11,324 --> 00:05:12,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay.</b></font>

89
00:05:12,884 --> 00:05:14,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>See how much you steered.</b></font>

90
00:05:14,894 --> 00:05:17,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sure.</b></font>

91
00:05:17,364 --> 00:05:20,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?! This is it?!</b></font>

92
00:05:20,834 --> 00:05:22,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I steered as far as I could.</b></font>

93
00:05:22,494 --> 00:05:23,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>See?</b></font>

94
00:05:23,704 --> 00:05:26,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How can you turn corners like this?</b></font>

95
00:05:26,534 --> 00:05:28,904
