98
00:05:35,374 --> 00:05:37,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--All the corners.
--What?!</b></font>

99
00:05:37,884 --> 00:05:42,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But Takumi is a drift expert, so he can manage.</b></font>

100
00:05:42,054 --> 00:05:44,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not that easy.</b></font>

101
00:05:44,054 --> 00:05:45,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You can't counter,</b></font>

102
00:05:45,724 --> 00:05:49,024
