106
00:06:00,904 --> 00:06:03,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--He drives an EG6, right?
--Yes.</b></font>

107
00:06:03,974 --> 00:06:08,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Its accelerator eliminates oversteering,</b></font>

108
00:06:08,044 --> 00:06:09,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so he can attack corners at full speed.</b></font>

109
00:06:09,514 --> 00:06:11,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Its side brake also eliminates "under."</b></font>

110
00:06:11,814 --> 00:06:14,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But an FR such as the Eight-Six
