116
00:06:35,534 --> 00:06:38,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Isn't that Kenji?
--Oh...</b></font>

117
00:06:40,074 --> 00:06:41,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Iketani...</b></font>

118
00:06:41,574 --> 00:06:46,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I did a little research on
that punk from the other day.</b></font>

119
00:06:46,114 --> 00:06:49,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's Shingo Shoji of the Myogi Night Kids.</b></font>

120
00:06:49,684 --> 00:06:51,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Shingo Shoji of the Night Kids...</b></font>

121
00:06:51,854 --> 00:06:54,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's their number two,</b></font>

122
00:06:54,124 --> 00:06:56,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but he's confident enough to call himself</b></font>

123
00:06:56,854 --> 00:07:00,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>the fastest downhill racer of the Night Kids.</b></font>

124
00:07:00,124 --> 00:07:02,564
